Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.14,0:03:17.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.60,0:03:19.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.03,0:03:20.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三
