Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.53,0:03:25.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,六
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.00,0:03:26.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,七
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.46,0:03:28.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,八
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.02,0:03:29.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,九
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.51,0:03:31.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一百
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.04,0:03:35.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.38,0:03:37.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.42,0:03:41.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去收拾
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.34,0:03:43.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一年级！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.37,0:03:44.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.15,0:03:57.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,摆振从头再做一次
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.98,0:03:59.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开始
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.85,0:04:00.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.81,0:04:06.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今年的剑道部好不得了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.96,0:04:10.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为换了个指导  练习超严格的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.73,0:04:12.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到去年为止都是个懒懒散散的部团呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.25,0:04:15.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连竹剑的打击声都没有
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.12,0:04:19.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.73,0:04:22.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说一年级都不少人陆续退出呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.39,0:04:24.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在搞那种热血…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.41,0:04:25.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本不时兴了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.09,0:04:31.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂！别停下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.44,0:04:36.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面——！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.36,0:04:42.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杉本
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.47,0:04:45.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上次大赛你初战就输掉了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.93,0:04:47.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被人击中面和腹部
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.34,0:04:49.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说说你为什么输
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.44,0:04:52.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对方排名在我前面…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.90,0:04:55.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的运气不好…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.94,0:04:57.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是理由
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.91,0:05:00.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我问你有什么地方不够
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.03,0:05:02.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,集中力不够！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.42,0:05:05.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以及练习不足
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.10,0:05:07.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好  那就进行更多的练习
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.01,0:05:08.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站起来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.57,0:05:12.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吓人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.17,0:05:13.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.10,0:05:14.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女生！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.43,0:05:16.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们在看什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.00,0:05:18.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下周不是还有练习赛吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.01,0:05:19.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,继续练习
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.31,0:05:21.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  是！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.73,0:05:23.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一年级还只能练摆振
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.06,0:05:26.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？少了两个人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.73,0:05:28.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,步美和美砂怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.31,0:05:31.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她们说太严格受不了就…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.88,0:05:32.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.65,0:05:37.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…一年级的退部了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.14,0:05:40.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想走的就让她们走
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.24,0:05:42.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,继续
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.32,0:05:43.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.75,0:05:48.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一年级剩下的女生就只有我们了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.52,0:05:51.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办  小望
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.94,0:05:53.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也退出好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.36,0:05:55.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说芽衣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.60,0:05:58.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是连你都走了  一年级不就只剩下我一个了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.83,0:06:01.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.10,0:06:09.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见  东同学
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.80,0:06:12.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  再见
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.84,0:06:14.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,东同学？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.87,0:06:16.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.03,0:06:20.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就是…东同学吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.70,0:06:25.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.16,0:06:27.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.28,0:06:29.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于见到了！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.86,0:06:31.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小东东！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.15,0:06:34.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了  我做了什么…？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.69,0:06:36.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来  我们走  小东东
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.67,0:06:37.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.30,0:06:38.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去哪里？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.44,0:06:39.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快一点快一点！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.59,0:06:43.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等  等等  你们给我说明一下…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.94,0:06:45.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们是剑道部的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.26,0:06:47.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剑道部…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.74,0:06:50.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小东东初中练过剑道吧？对吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.54,0:06:54.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且还很强对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.81,0:06:57.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说  加入剑道部啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.54,0:06:58.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放弃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.25,0:07:00.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小次郎老师
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.94,0:07:03.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她不会加入剑道社的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.54,0:07:04.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.21,0:07:06.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对吧  东
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.14,0:07:08.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…是的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.16,0:07:10.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么为什么为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.41,0:07:13.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你其实不喜欢剑道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.81,0:07:15.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有那回事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.69,0:07:17.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我从小就很喜欢…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.43,0:07:22.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是…父母说上高中后就不能再练
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.37,0:07:25.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我自己也这么决定的…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.65,0:07:28.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以  真的非常抱歉…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.07,0:07:30.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是为什么啊  小东东？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.01,0:07:32.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太可惜了！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.26,0:07:33.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞不好太可惜妖怪都要跑出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.21,0:07:35.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该说  已经跑出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.13,0:07:39.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太可惜啦！太可惜啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.73,0:07:43.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  就是这样…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.69,0:07:44.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我告辞了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.37,0:07:52.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就当参观一下跟我们走嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.08,0:07:56.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从小就很喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.60,0:07:58.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要让她参观一下部团活动的话
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.41,0:08:00.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她一定会想继续练习下去的！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.79,0:08:02.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦咯！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.64,0:08:03.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪里  万分荣幸！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.40,0:08:06.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.42,0:08:11.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…为什么我要穿上防具…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.05,0:08:13.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是说只参观一下…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.33,0:08:17.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要想回去的活
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.40,0:08:18.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必须打倒我们两个哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.20,0:08:21.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不然是出不去的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.40,0:08:27.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.79,0:08:40.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我就…奉陪一下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.15,0:08:41.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉呀？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.35,0:08:45.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,川添同学  我去拿簸箕来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.90,0:08:46.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.16,0:08:50.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.58,0:08:56.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像要下雨了  小都都
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.14,0:08:59.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕  我今天没带伞
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.24,0:09:02.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,部室里面有的  不用担心
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.75,0:09:06.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这声音…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.68,0:09:19.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纪梨乃前辈吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.96,0:09:25.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…不是  那是谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.06,0:09:29.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.17,0:09:31.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面击！好漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.06,0:09:33.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过那是谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.92,0:09:39.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面——！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.58,0:09:41.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,腹——！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.41,0:09:46.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好…好赞
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.00,0:09:49.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行了  东
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.93,0:09:50.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  好的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.30,0:09:52.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,东？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.42,0:09:58.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鞘
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.01,0:10:00.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纪梨乃
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.74,0:10:02.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她好强呢～
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.09,0:10:04.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯～
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.42,0:10:06.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,东  你什么时候开始练剑道的？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.84,0:10:08.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从小学开始
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.36,0:10:11.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有经验  技术也棒
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.86,0:10:13.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好想要…好想要但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.08,0:10:15.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.12,0:10:15.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.86,0:10:17.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可以回去了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.95,0:10:20.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  不好意思  耽搁你的时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.37,0:10:22.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶  要回去了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.93,0:10:23.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.71,0:10:26.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能再耽误你一点时间吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.74,0:10:28.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和我比一场吧  东同学
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.65,0:10:29.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.58,0:10:30.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闪亮～
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.12,0:10:33.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁比较厉害啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.50,0:10:36.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然是勇次君咯  他是男孩子嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.68,0:10:39.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎哟  不要小看小东东哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.88,0:10:43.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对对  要知道我们是没赢一局啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.13,0:10:45.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.10,0:10:50.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不再赶回去念书的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.19,0:11:28.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好强啊  小东东
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.30,0:11:31.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然最后还是勇次连得两分…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.20,0:11:35.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女生对上勇次君打成那样很厉害了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.85,0:11:39.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果再继续下去的话  搞不好我会被拿下一分
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.78,0:11:41.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我突然提出这样的要求嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.49,0:11:43.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的确啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.58,0:11:47.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是她是第五人的话我就放心多了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.52,0:11:48.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是嘛！就是嘛！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.43,0:11:52.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绿色终于要定下来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.38,0:11:54.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这下子就能正常地进行团体战了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.58,0:11:57.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们不听人说话吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.18,0:12:00.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,东她是不会加入剑道社的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.64,0:12:01.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.56,0:12:03.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我不会让她加入的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.43,0:12:04.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说啥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.06,0:12:07.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说想让她加入的人不是你吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.75,0:12:09.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道啊  笨蛋！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.43,0:12:12.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不甘心啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.38,0:12:16.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是必须放弃啊！把东忘记吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.55,0:12:19.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是…她可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.92,0:12:23.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.10,0:12:26.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,东的考试成绩
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.27,0:12:28.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很糟糕吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.93,0:12:31.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃…确实很糟糕…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.42,0:12:34.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她非常认真  从没有请假或者迟到
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.49,0:12:36.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上课也都认真听讲做笔记
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.82,0:12:39.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但还是很糟糕吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.58,0:12:41.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…确实很糟糕
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.39,0:12:47.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她不是不会念书  入学考试的时候也有像样的分数
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.09,0:12:54.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只不过不是迷糊到弄错考试范围  就是答题把答案写错行
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.18,0:12:56.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果继续练剑道的话
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.24,0:13:00.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成绩可能又要再掉一级
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.59,0:13:05.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她想要考上大学
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.17,0:13:11.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,石田老师  请你不要强求她加入剑道部了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.67,0:13:13.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.35,0:13:29.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是…她可是…没办法参加啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.92,0:13:35.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她要更加努力念书  提高成绩才行啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.57,0:13:40.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然不是很清楚  但只有放弃小东东咯？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.37,0:13:42.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本人没这个意思的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.08,0:13:46.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她一定不想再练剑道了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.16,0:13:48.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没那回事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.29,0:13:51.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我用竹剑与她交流过  所以很清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.46,0:13:53.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,东她非常喜欢剑道
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.80,0:13:57.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她的身体内有着火热的剑道之魂
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.97,0:14:01.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她绝对会以剑士的身份回到这里！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.04,0:14:04.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦～
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.98,0:14:05.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.82,0:14:11.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,课本和练习册都忘带回来了！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.92,0:14:14.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,写不了作业了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.45,0:14:19.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天累死人了…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.82,0:14:27.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面——！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.74,0:14:29.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,腹——！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.83,0:14:40.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和我比一场吧  东同学
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.61,0:14:45.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行不行
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.39,0:14:47.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要用功读书
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.38,0:14:53.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次考试的目标是…平均分！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.78,0:14:56.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和我比一场吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.78,0:15:06.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是东聪莉  本篇里也在朝着平均分努力着！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.23,0:15:09.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说  还没人接吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.85,0:15:11.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不快一点赶不及啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.66,0:15:13.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.63,0:15:14.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  小望！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.08,0:15:17.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在哪里？快点来啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.53,0:15:19.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家已经到车站了  比赛…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.78,0:15:20.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  芽衣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.90,0:15:22.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我放弃剑道了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.45,0:15:27.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们走  时间到了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.23,0:15:29.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能让对方等
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.76,0:15:33.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小望  喂喂？喂喂？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.73,0:15:36.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芽衣  你今天也出场比赛吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.92,0:15:37.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.97,0:15:40.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为现在只剩下五个人了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.02,0:15:48.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.85,0:15:51.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经说了不用你一定要加入啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.54,0:15:53.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以就拜托你最后再来一次咯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.97,0:15:56.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次的练习赛来我们这里吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.85,0:15:59.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是看看  之后我们就不再缠你啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.92,0:16:00.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.11,0:16:06.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,东同学  前辈们这么期待  你就再来一次如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.92,0:16:07.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或者说…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.83,0:16:10.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必须给我来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.65,0:16:14.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可怕…那个人到底是什么做的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.01,0:16:18.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是…对不起了！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.59,0:16:21.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.04,0:16:23.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  哟
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.21,0:16:25.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了  要回去了？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.05,0:16:28.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个…那个…我是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.01,0:16:30.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.85,0:16:35.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都跑来这里了  就进去看看啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.59,0:16:38.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.21,0:16:41.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是小东东！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.57,0:16:43.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能来太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.90,0:16:48.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  有一半给人感觉是威吓一样  还是有点那个啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.04,0:16:50.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但一般那样是不会来的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.98,0:16:53.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是真的讨厌的话
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.91,0:17:05.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是…小都的…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.65,0:17:10.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.56,0:17:12.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请问是室江高中剑道部的人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.75,0:17:15.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  是的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.85,0:17:17.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是成明高中的人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.31,0:17:19.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为今天的比赛所以过来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.13,0:17:22.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是突然下雨很是烦恼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.45,0:17:24.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能让我避一下雨吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.71,0:17:26.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  可以
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.16,0:17:30.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂…喂  你靠太近了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.73,0:17:35.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种时候让小都看见了会怎么样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.84,0:17:42.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快看快看！小都快看这里！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.82,0:17:46.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  那是什么？野山栗？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.52,0:17:49.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,段郎  要不我们回去吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.04,0:17:55.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了小都都  身体不舒服吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.25,0:17:57.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  不是那样…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.46,0:18:00.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但有些不好的预感
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.75,0:18:05.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不去怎么可以呢  本来人就不够
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.93,0:18:07.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  那个没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.36,0:18:10.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为找了个可爱的孩子来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.67,0:18:12.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以就算我不去也没事…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.99,0:18:14.95,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行不行我们走
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.97,0:18:17.41,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  稍微等我一下啦  段郎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.01,0:18:18.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？是宫崎同学和荣花同学
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.93,0:18:21.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们两个是什么关系？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.84,0:18:23.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男女朋友啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.82,0:18:24.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.82,0:18:28.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很要好的  总是粘在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.55,0:18:32.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男朋友…女朋友？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.54,0:18:36.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来  其他的部员呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.03,0:18:50.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  小东东呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.68,0:18:51.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在哪里？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.95,0:18:52.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.95,0:18:55.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我只是来参观…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.90,0:18:59.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然还是穿上道服才能平静心灵啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.59,0:19:02.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难得来一次  防具也一起穿上吧～
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.12,0:19:09.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么  为什么会有这样的装备！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.74,0:19:10.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别在意
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.17,0:19:12.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  很配哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.64,0:19:16.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天我也来担当裁判
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.55,0:19:18.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勇次怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.56,0:19:20.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  是有点…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.03,0:19:23.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小都都也…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.53,0:19:25.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  没什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.25,0:19:33.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打扰了  我是成明高中摄影部的小田岛礼美  来进行摄影
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.54,0:19:34.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才的！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.72,0:19:36.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  那么请进
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.02,0:19:38.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.90,0:19:44.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小都～笑一个
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.34,0:19:48.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,礼美  礼美
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.53,0:19:50.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁来着
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.65,0:19:53.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是何方神圣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.06,0:19:54.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,石田老师
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.73,0:19:57.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芳川老师  你怎么来了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.29,0:20:00.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为听说有练习赛有点在意…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.21,0:20:03.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让她参观没问题吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.25,0:20:07.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来  请进请进
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.92,0:20:08.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.09,0:20:21.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鄙姓石田  今天请林老师多多指教了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.79,0:20:23.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这边才是  请多多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.85,0:20:29.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前就听说过您的大名了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.63,0:20:31.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能和老师的学生进行练习赛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.34,0:20:34.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对我们来说也是个很好的学习机会
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.75,0:20:35.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不敢当
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.72,0:20:38.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像很愉快呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.72,0:20:45.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思  我们的部员太懒散
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.73,0:20:49.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该是我太放纵他们的错吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.62,0:20:53.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都不知道怎么办呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.90,0:20:56.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个年龄段的孩子都很复杂呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.53,0:20:59.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比赛要开始了  快点带上头盔
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.72,0:21:01.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.15,0:21:08.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然要出场比赛…这该怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.29,0:21:10.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芽衣  你是次锋
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.15,0:21:12.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.92,0:21:19.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是输掉比赛  老师又要发火了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.42,0:21:23.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说说你为什么输
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.44,0:21:26.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我问你有什么地方不够
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.54,0:21:31.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不够的地方…根本没有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.68,0:21:35.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是陪朋友才加入的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.47,0:21:38.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我对剑道也没什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.37,0:21:40.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放弃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.80,0:21:43.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等比赛结束后  我也要…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.99,0:21:46.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,准备好了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.90,0:21:47.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.75,0:21:51.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.28,0:21:55.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  练习和我一组好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.17,0:21:59.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的  请多多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.04,0:22:01.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.73,0:22:13.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请多指教了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.30,0:22:14.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手下留情哦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.92,0:22:16.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  很期待啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.70,0:22:17.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.18,0:22:19.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么开始
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.94,0:22:22.62,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fs24\fad(300,0)}I'm Calling the STAR RISE
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.85,0:22:27.64,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}夕闇に  輝き出す  願いたち
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.94,0:22:34.03,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}この手の中 降りてきて 流れ星…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.06,0:22:55.09,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}窓辺で素足のまま  夜を見上げて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.54,0:23:02.12,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}眠れない 月明かり ひとり
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.99,0:23:09.99,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}目の前を ちらついてく 昼間の私
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.60,0:23:17.33,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}自分だけ 空回りで もどかしいまま
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.61,0:23:20.29,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fs24}I'm Calling the STAR RISE
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.58,0:23:25.33,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}目を閉じて  心の声  聞いてる
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.62,0:23:32.17,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}まだ知らない 私に出会いたい
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.33,0:23:35.17,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fs24}I'm Calling the STAR RISE
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.42,0:23:40.17,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}まばゆく  輝いてる  願いたち
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.50,0:23:47.85,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}この手の中 降りてきて 流れ星…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.94,0:22:22.62,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(300,0)}I'm Calling the STAR RISE
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.85,0:22:27.64,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}暮色中闪耀着的那小小心愿
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.94,0:22:34.03,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}寄于手中  希望流星能为我实现…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.06,0:22:55.09,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}在窗边光着脚丫  仰望着夜空
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.54,0:23:02.12,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}唯有无法入眠的月光相伴
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.99,0:23:09.99,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}眼前浮现出午时的自己
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.60,0:23:17.33,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}只是徒劳得令人着急
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.61,0:23:20.29,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'm Calling the STAR RISE
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.58,0:23:25.33,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}闭上眼睛倾听心中的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.62,0:23:32.17,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}依然无法得知  它想与我相见
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.33,0:23:35.17,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'm Calling the STAR RISE
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.42,0:23:40.17,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}光辉而耀眼的那小小心愿
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.50,0:23:47.85,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}寄于手中  希望流星能为我实现…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.50,0:23:51.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是东聪莉
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.92,0:23:54.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于在本篇中正式登场了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.37,0:23:56.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之后我会继续活跃…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.18,0:23:59.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？已经播放结束了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.01,0:24:02.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那就不靠集数靠密度来决胜负吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.20,0:24:03.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集是…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.63,0:24:10.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,眼镜…眼镜眼镜…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.86,0:24:16.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下…下集是「东的情况同芽衣的情况」
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.30,0:24:19.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃…那是这一话的！
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.52,0:24:20.05,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（下集  老师们和学生们）
